    "description": "《Love, Ghostie》是一款闲适模拟经营游戏，内含大量治愈系浪漫故事！你将化身庄园里的可爱幽灵，任务就是为住户牵线搭桥，帮他们找到真爱！<br><br>你会创造出怎样的爱情故事呢？<br><br>一局游戏约需3到6小时，具体取决于你是想试验组合各种CP，还是直接撮合心仪的CP。一局游戏可以促成6对CP，所以至少玩够11次才能解锁所有可见的内容！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2>♥随心拉郎配——每位住户都能和其他任何住户组CP！<br><br>♥了解每位住户的独特个性——读他们的日记，送他们礼物，以此发现他们最爱的事物！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/e64489c9f49a4dc8b9804b194dc4b5d6.poster.avif?t=1764037337\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/e64489c9f49a4dc8b9804b194dc4b5d6.webm?t=1764037337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/e64489c9f49a4dc8b9804b194dc4b5d6.mp4?t=1764037337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>♥让陌生人的生活重焕愉悦——给住户们安排（不那么）秘密的约会，帮他们装饰房间，派他们完成任务，以此振奋他们的精神！<br><br>♥帮住户找到灵魂伴侣——随着住户们的关系逐渐升温，你会解锁一幕幕可爱的恋爱场景。每对住户都有独特的故事！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/3d797d3402544c01440b188a314a24b1.poster.avif?t=1764037337\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/3d797d3402544c01440b188a314a24b1.webm?t=1764037337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/3d797d3402544c01440b188a314a24b1.mp4?t=1764037337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>♥玩转人心——通过可解锁的小游戏，增进住户感情，提升住户幸福感！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/eb8ab8feca493a6f61d5bd0ddc2096cf.poster.avif?t=1764037337\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/eb8ab8feca493a6f61d5bd0ddc2096cf.webm?t=1764037337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/eb8ab8feca493a6f61d5bd0ddc2096cf.mp4?t=1764037337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>♥海量CP组合——游戏中共有12名住户，可以探索多达66种CP配对，每对都有独特的故事线！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/d9cef801fa7675248b72f46e00f1b53c.poster.avif?t=1764037337\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/d9cef801fa7675248b72f46e00f1b53c.webm?t=1764037337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/d9cef801fa7675248b72f46e00f1b53c.mp4?t=1764037337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>♥让你的媒人技能更上一层楼——解锁小游戏、庄园升级、幽灵帽等有趣内容！<br><br>♥新游戏+模式——还没牵完所有的线？记忆板会保留你在之前游戏中解锁的约会和恋爱对话。其他新游戏+功能助力你更快推进恋爱关系！",
